# Enforce Authentication on Game Pages

This plan aims to prevent users from accessing specific game pages if they are not signed in.

## Proposed Changes

We will add a check for the `loggedInEmail` in `localStorage` at the beginning of each game's main JavaScript file. If the email is missing (meaning the user is not logged in), they will be redirected to the root `index.html`.

