The following block will be added after the "Fresh Session Check":

```javascript
// --- Authentication Check ---
if (!localStorage.getItem('loggedInEmail')) {
    window.location.href = '/';
}
```

## Verification Plan

### Manual Verification
- Attempt to access any of the game URLs directly while not logged in.
- Verify that the browser redirects to the landing page (`index.html`).
- Log in and verify that the game pages are accessible normally.
